        <item>
            <title>《日经中文网》 X 帐号简体中文转繁体，简体字网民：繁体中文如厌烦的蛆虫</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/chinese-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chinese-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/chinese-2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 08:52:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《日经新闻》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[简体字]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[繁体字]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203378</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《日本经济新闻》继最近在官网中推出繁体中文版本的语言选择外，《日经中文网》在昨日（6 日）在社交媒体 X 中宣布，即日起帐号将会尝试使用繁体字。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203384" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-3.36.46-PM-694x307.png" alt="" width="694" height="307" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-3.36.46-PM-694x307.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-3.36.46-PM-768x340.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-3.36.46-PM.png 1188w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《日经中文网》是编制日经指数的《日本经济新闻》的中文版。在昨日之前《日经中文网》在 X 中的帖文皆以简体中文书写及发布，但在发出转用繁体字的公告后，大致所有文章皆改以使用繁体中文来书写。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203386" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.03.55-PM-e1699344351989-694x114.png" alt="" width="694" height="114" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.03.55-PM-e1699344351989-694x114.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.03.55-PM-e1699344351989-768x127.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.03.55-PM-e1699344351989.png 1182w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203389" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.10.13-PM-694x156.png" alt="" width="694" height="156" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.10.13-PM-694x156.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.10.13-PM-768x172.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.10.13-PM.png 1194w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在该公告的帖文底下，有许多两岸的网民皆表达支持以及反对的看法。</p><p>有使用简体字的网民讽刺，建议《日经中文网》转用甲骨文、篆体等的字体，看起来比繁体字更像正体字，甚至有网民留言指繁体字字体繁复，写在纸上犹如一堆令人厌烦的蛆虫。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203388" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.07.13-PM-694x224.png" alt="" width="694" height="224" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.07.13-PM-694x224.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.07.13-PM-768x247.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.07.13-PM.png 1186w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203390" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.13.57-PM-694x458.png" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.13.57-PM-694x458.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.13.57-PM-768x506.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-07-at-4.13.57-PM.png 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>但亦有网民支持本次的措施，有留言指繁体字的字形优美，值得承传；又指本次的改变的拨乱反正，希望《日经中文网》不只尝试，直接改为使用繁体字发布文章。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/rijingzhongwen/status/1721331675106574500">Twitter</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/chinese-2/fun-tech/">《日经中文网》 X 帐号简体中文转繁体，简体字网民：繁体中文如厌烦的蛆虫</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
