        <item>
            <title>香港 NFT 活动导致参加者视力受损　主办单位：只有少于 1% 参加者出事</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/bored-ape-eye-vision-problems-apefest-hong-kong/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bored-ape-eye-vision-problems-apefest-hong-kong</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/bored-ape-eye-vision-problems-apefest-hong-kong/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:14:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NFT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203303</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>大型活动的安全绝对不容忽视，不过近年越来越多相关问题出现，最近在香港举办的 Yuga Labs ApeFest 就发生参加者视力受损的意外。<br /><span id="more-1203303"></span></p><p>据报导指，无聊猿 BAYC 在香港举办的 ApeFest 活动刚刚结束不久后，有至少 15 名参加者表示其照明效果导致眼部烧伤、视力损害以及极度疼痛，甚至需要半夜去医院急症治疗。这些视力受损的参加者都是站在靠近舞台位置的人，受到强烈灯光照射。</p><p>主办单位 Yuga Labs 表示，他们已经了解这情况，正在联络受影响人士以及进行调查了解原因，强调当时有约 2,250 参加者和工作人员在场，只有少于 1% 的人报告类似情况。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Woke up in the middle of the night after Apefest with so much pain in my eyes that I had to go to the hospital. I&#39;ve seen several tweets about it</p><p>Doctor told me it was due to the UV from stage lights. I go to festivals often but have never experienced this</p><p>I try to understand…</p><p>&mdash; Crypto June 💎🎯 (@CryptoJune777) <a href="https://twitter.com/CryptoJune777/status/1721093778176614697?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 5, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>有分析认为这次意外与「光害性角膜炎」有关，也就是所谓的「雪盲症」，一般会在眼睛过度暴露于紫外线下，导致结膜和角膜发炎。在 2017 年 HypeBeast 的派对中就因为使用了大量 UV 消毒灯泡充当环境等效，导致多人烧伤和视力受损。今次是否同样的问题则仍然有待调查。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://cointelegraph.com/news/bored-ape-eye-vision-problems-apefest-hong-kong-lighting">Cointelegraph</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/07/bored-ape-eye-vision-problems-apefest-hong-kong/fun-tech/">香港 NFT 活动导致参加者视力受损　主办单位：只有少于 1% 参加者出事</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
